  'free-guide-7-money-mistakes', 'free-guide-7-money-mistakes', 'The 7 Money Mistakes That Keep Many Ghanaians Broke', 'A free, practical guide to the seven money mistakes keeping many Ghanaians stuck, with one honest fix and one immediate action for each. No jargon, no hype, no get-rich-quick promises.', 'This free guide walks through the seven money mistakes Robayer WealthLab sees most often among young professionals, National Service personnel, graduates, small business owners, and salaried workers across Ghana: spending without a plan, treating saving as whatever is left over, having no emergency fund, avoiding investing because it feels complicated, letting lifestyle grow as fast as income, depending on a single source of income, and not understanding good debt versus bad debt.

Each chapter follows the same structure: the mistake itself, why it happens, what it looks like in a real Ghanaian context, and one honest, doable fix, closing with a one-page Quick Wealth Checklist and a next step into the flagship guide, Small Cedis, Big Wealth.',
